506
00:32:06,658 --> 00:32:08,625
Oh, you see, we happen to have got
here in the middle of the night...

507
00:32:08,694 --> 00:32:10,331
Yes, I noticed. You
busted down my fence.

508
00:32:10,356 --> 00:32:11,734
Oh, I'll be glad
